org.tros.utils

Class TypeHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.tros.utils.TypeHandler

  • public final class TypeHandler
extends Object
    Provides conversion from one object type to another. Often this is date to/from String. Color to/from String. But bean utils is used to do just about anything under the sun.
    Author:
    matta
